high_descs: Pick up the pot on the left of the stove.
Bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Bring the pot to the stove.
Put the pot on the front left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the front left of the stove.

high_descs: move towards the counter and turn right to face the stove
pick up the pot from the left back burner of the stove
turn to the right, move towards and face the refrigerator
open the fridge door, put the pot on the top shelf and close the door for three seconds and then open the door and pick up the pot
close the fridge door, turn around and go across the room and turn to face the stove
put the pot on the front left burner of the stove
anns.task_desc: put a chilled pot on the front left burner of the stove

high_descs: Walk across the room to the counter and take a right to get to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the left side of the stove in the back.
Turn and walk over to the fridge.
Cool off the pot in the fridge and take it back out.
Turn around and take the chilled pot back across the room to the stove.
Set the chilled pot down on the front left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the stove.
